# Bugs and Issues

This folder contains documentation for bugs and issues.

## What Goes Here

- Issue-XXX-[Description].md files documenting bugs

## Creating a New Issue

1. Find the next issue number (check existing files)
2. Create: `Issue-XXX-Brief-Description.md`
3. Include:
   - Description of the issue
   - Steps to reproduce
   - Expected vs actual behavior
   - Screenshots or error messages (if applicable)
   - Resolution (once fixed)

## Example

```markdown
# Issue-042: Login Button Unresponsive on iOS

## Description
The login button on the sign-in screen does not respond to taps on iOS devices.

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open the app on an iOS device
2. Navigate to the sign-in screen
3. Enter credentials
4. Tap the "Log In" button

## Expected Behavior
Button should trigger login flow.

## Actual Behavior
Nothing happens. No visual feedback, no network request.

## Environment
- iOS 17.2
- iPhone 14 Pro
- App version 1.2.3

## Resolution
Fixed in commit abc123. The touchable area was too small.
```
